                        <interp inst="t18390916-name-286" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE SOWARD</persName>
                  </hi>. I am assistant to Mr. Aldous. I took in this gun of Johnson..</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was a little in liquor, I saw the gun outside, and I took it-if it had been inside I should not have done it.</p>
